8 hours at 00:00, 08:00, and 16:00 UTC using a time-weighted average premium over the funding period. The exchange caps funding rates at ±0.75% per interval to prevent extreme payments. Funding settlements occur automatically in USDT, with long positions paying when rates are positive and receiving payments when negative. Phemex's funding rate formula incorporates both premium and interest rate components, typically resulting in rates between -0.1% to +0.3% for FIL."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
